{"id":286797,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-上海维权人士魏勤寻衅滋事案被移送/","date":"2013-03-30T12:46:03Z","modified":"2013-03-30T12:46:03Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权人士魏勤“寻衅滋事”案被移送检察院（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员亦然报道）本网获悉，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>被上海市公安局闸北分局以“涉嫌聚众扰乱公共场所秩序”罪刑事拘留，同年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>被以“寻衅滋事”罪逮捕的维权人士魏勤一案，于同年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>已经移送到检察院，被逮捕半年以来，魏勤一直羁押在上海市静安区看守所内。本月中旬，北京莫少平律师事务所的尚宝军律师受其亲属委托，到看守所会见了魏勤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，上海市公安局静安分局指控，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>，魏勤与王扣玛等人以祭奠王扣玛的母亲为由，在王扣玛的家中设灵堂、烧纸钱，并呼喊“还我人权，还我母亲，还我公道”的口号，造成严重的社会影响。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另警方指控魏勤，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>，魏勤及他人以悼念陈小明五周年祭日为由，魏勤带头呼喊出轨的口号‘打倒共产党’等煽动性口号，造成极其恶劣的社会影响。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>魏勤被羁押半年以来，无法得到任何外界的信息，家人更不能获知她在看守所内的身体健康情况。尚宝军律师的会见，令魏勤喜出望外，她表示感谢律师及各界人士的帮助。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2002</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月，魏勤工作多年被工厂无故辞退，生活陷入困境。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2002</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月居住地又遭遇动迁（举世关注的东八块地段），</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>住房被非法强拆，从此走上充满血泪的上访之路。魏勤不但自己依法维权，还为其他权益受到侵犯的人维权，并成为零八宪章的首批签署人之一。因此遭到监控、行政拘留、劳教等迫害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>魏勤被抓捕后，上海及各地维权人士多次为其呼吁并捐款。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-dlr47oCAKvU/UVZU-r5_KfI/AAAAAAAAfhA/g2Mf0FuuRtw/s1600/%E9%AD%8F.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"196\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-dlr47oCAKvU/UVZU-r5_KfI/AAAAAAAAfhA/g2Mf0FuuRtw/s320/%E9%AD%8F.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span><span></span><span></span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}